    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330350/extras/71435bcd680719d82fe3b2951b0e4a82.poster.avif?t=1765469182\" width=800 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330350/extras/71435bcd680719d82fe3b2951b0e4a82.webm?t=1765469182\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330350/extras/71435bcd680719d82fe3b2951b0e4a82.mp4?t=1765469182\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> A new approach to representing Athletics and Track mechanics in gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against other sprinters in different modes and tournaments to fill your trophy cabinet and unlock new gear .</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple modes are available to the player:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new Training ground mode help new comers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Time Trial Mode to challenge players and unlock reward</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick races can be done in single player or with local 2 player</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hermes Quest:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Participate at this new original tournament with a created sprinter and strive for Gold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Locations, both indoors and outdoors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Race Types ranging from the 60 meters to the 400 meters relay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
